OL,3,C'Blood on your hands': Mother warns
OL,4,Cintoxicated drivers after son killed
OL,6,FA mother who lost her son to a drunk
OL,7,Fdriver says anyone who lets drunk or
OL,8,Fdrugged drivers behind the wheel, has
OL,9,F"blood on their hands".
OL,11,FClaire Chapman's son Harry died after
OL,12,Fhis car was hit by a drunk driver
OL,13,Falong Aldridge Road in Streetly in
OL,14,FBirmingham on October 7, 2022.
OL,16,FHe had been bowling with his sister
OL,17,Fand making plans to celebrate his 21st
OL,18,Fbirthday with his best friend on the
OL,19,Fnight of the crash.
