OL,3,C'Blood on your hands': Mother warns
OL,4,Cintoxicated drivers after son killed
OL,6,FAfter dropping his friend home, his
OL,7,Fcar was hit by the drunk driver who
OL,8,Fwas traveling at 97mph in a 30 zone
OL,9,Fand driving the wrong side of the road.
OL,11,FThe drunk driver was sentenced to 11
OL,12,Fyears and three months in prison.
OL,14,FClaire is now backing a police
OL,15,Fcampaign to catch drivers under the
OL,16,Finfluence.
OL,18,FClaire said: "I felt like I gave a
OL,19,Fpiece of my soul. But today is more
OL,20,Fabout accountability, today is more
OL,21,Fabout being sensible.
