OL,3,C'Blood on your hands': Mother warns
OL,4,Cintoxicated drivers after son killed
OL,6,F"Go out and have a good time but just
OL,7,Fdon't put somebody else in the firing
OL,8,Fline. It all starts with you, it all
OL,9,Fstarts with you as an individual and
OL,10,FI've said it before and I'll say it
OL,11,Fagain anybody that allows someone to
OL,12,Fdrive drunk, you have blood on your
OL,13,Fhands. You are as guilty as that
OL,14,Fperson."
OL,16,FWest Midlands Police say if you see
OL,17,Fsomeone who is going to drink or drug
OL,18,Fdrive take their keys off them or if
OL,19,Fyou can't stop them then call 999.
